      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThis is an updated version of http://review.whamcloud.com/10481, which was landed but later reverted due to problems with Oleg's test environment.\n\nI suspect that was caused by /sbin being read-only on his system, which is why it did not cause problems on my system or autotest.  I've changed the code to not try to modify /sbin/mount.lustre if it is not writable.",
